Summary: saw object flat as a pancake moving thru the sky
divs: Sighting Details i was walking across the street when somethingjust seemed to attract my attention. i looked up and saw what i thought at firtwas a bundle of baloons.it was obviously not a aircraft or helicopter. but itwas windy that morning and at first it was stationary. once it began to move itstarted doing rotations and i could see it was totally flat, that to me ruledout balloons.i watched it for a few minutes until it just vanished. my feelingswere i saw something else. i reported another sighting to mufon a few years backout of houston texas. i reported under my first name bradley heath jones.
